<font color="#FF0000">REPLY TO PROFESSOR GRIVETTI</font><br>
<tt>Mon Jan 20 14:58:56 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Thank you very much for the site information. Will check it out.<br><br>
Am currently president of VVA Liberty Bell Chapter #266, which has 210 members from all sorts of military backgrounds. Am a past president of Philadelphia/English Chapter, Association of the 173rd Airborne Brigade; currently Assistant Chaplain, Philadelphia United Veterans' Council; member of Vietnam Helicopter Crewmembers Association (am one of very few officers with an aircrewmember's badge) and Catholic War Veterans. As you can see, am a bit of a joiner and will probably meet myself coming and going one of these days.<br><br>
Marsha Four, the executive director of Philadelphia Standdown (modeled after San Diego's program to assist homeless vets) is active in VVA in this area. She was a nurse in country and knows others. I will convey your request to her.
